{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-7","id":"msg_01Q67dUPLqaaoSCDTreMyf2N","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"All four check commands pass: ruff check, ruff format --check, pytest (278 passed), and mypy.\n\nImplemented `validate_plan` at `bob_tools/planfile/operations.py:27`:\n\n- `_iter_tasks` recursively yields every Task in a tuple, descending into `children`.\n- `_iter_plan_tasks` walks all task containers: phase tasks, subsection tasks, and bugs.\n- `validate_plan(plan)` collects every known `task_id`, then walks every task's `deps` and raises `PlanValidationError` with one message per missing reference (does not short-circuit). Tasks without a `task_id` (compat mode) still have their deps checked; the error message falls back to source line number.\n\nTests in `bob_tools/planfile/tests/test_operations.py` cover: empty plan, no-deps plans, deps resolving to siblings/nested children/bugs/subsections, unknown deps raising at root/nested/subsection/bug positions, multiple errors aggregated, and the `task_id=None` fallback message."}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":655,"cache_read_input_tokens":81486,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":655},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"6dee31ca-fa09-4e8e-86c1-f9acdefe892d","uuid":"7b1fb599-4d27-4a3c-a7d5-06ced38c532c"}
